{"tid":1998660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［林鄭會唔會又支持］郭富城下星期開網上演唱會為跳舞業界籌款","createTime":"2020-05-02T14:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:46:49.000Z","uid":242050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f6476839653d921dbb527ee6d1da15db655408a","tid":1998660,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYqSqfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYqSqfb.png&h=a98f57a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n演唱會由《健康&middot;旦》及「郭富城國際關愛慈善基金」主辦，《蘋果》向製作人蕭潮順求證時，他承認說：「係，城城會繼阿Sam之後喺同一個地方開騷，今次係籌款騷，但捐款會直接捐去郭富城國際關愛慈善基金，城城今次好想幫助佢身邊合作多年一班dancers同埋電影界同業，詳情稍後會公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCxabVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCxabVK.jpg&h=34a82c82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzCabVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzCabVK.jpg&h=c853d654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20200502/60897053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200502%2F60897053&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=4b282754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200502%2F60897053&h=00b69283\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20200502/60897053</a>"},{"pid":"f3d84ac3b4c844f911dfeae82ededfef6874ccbd","tid":1998660,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溫馨提示提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">西樹泡芙係藍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日見到超級多後生女排買二送二個優惠<br />\n可能有啲人未知<br />\n但希望如果知道嘅人以後搵其他嘢取代<img src=\"/a